# Title: Arbitrary File Download Via PresentationHost.EXE
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2022-08-19
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects usage of "PresentationHost" which is a utility that runs ".xbap" (Browser Applications) files to download arbitrary files
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.execution, attack.stealth, attack.t1218
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_presentationhost_download.yml

CommandLine IN ("*http://*", "*https://*", "*ftp://*") Image="*\\presentationhost.exe" OR OriginalFileName="PresentationHost.exe"